ICNS creation mini-howto
------------------------

This is how to create SVG to ICO:

1. Use inkscape.
2. Save into PNG format for the following sizes:
   16, 20, 24, 32, 40, 48, 64, 96, 256.
3. Use ImageMagick convert by entering all PNGs
   and choose the "ico" format as output.

This is how to convert ICO into ICNS:

1. Start Firefox and go to http://iconverticons.com/.
2. Go to Options, tick ICNS output.
3. Upload the ICO and convert.

Zoltan, 2012-09-15 and later
